a.n: The Babysitter 5: Lily Carter & Mr. Marcus

p.k: Stay at home mom Michelle Lay is worried about finances, and tells overworked husband Mr. Marcus that it's time to hire a babysitter so she can go back to work. But Lily wants more from her job than just pocket money, and soon the teen vixen is obsessing over sexy Dad Marcus. Written and directed by Nica Noelle.
